# Reusability Patterns

> **Version:** 1.0.0 | **Category:** Cat 4 (Patterns) | **TrigMem Auto-Load**
> **Triggers:** "barrel export", "shared component", "reuse", "generic type"
> **Last Updated:** 2026-03-18

---

## 🎯 Core Principle

**Code not reused is code wasted.** Every piece should be reusable.

---

## 📦 Barrel Exports

**Standard:** Always use index.ts

```typescript
// ✅ Pattern
export { Button } from './atoms/Button'
export { Card } from './molecules/Card'
export { Input } from './atoms/Input'
```

---

## 🧩 Component Reusability

### Variant Props

```typescript
type ButtonVariant = 'primary' | 'secondary' | 'ghost' | 'danger'
type ButtonSize = 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg'

export function Button({ variant, size, children, ...props }: ButtonProps) {
  // ... variant implementation
}
```

### Composition Slots

```typescript
export function Card({ header, body, footer, children }: CardProps) {
  return (
    <div class="card">
      {header && <div class="card-header">{header}</div>}
      {body ? <div class="card-body">{body}</div> : children}
      {footer && <div class="card-footer">{footer}</div>}
    </div>
  )
}
```

---

## 🔧 Utility Reusability

### Pure Functions

```typescript
export function formatCurrency(
  amount: number,
  currency = 'EUR',
  locale = 'fr-FR'
): string {
  return new Intl.NumberFormat(locale, {
    style: 'currency',
    currency
  }).format(amount)
}
```

### Generic Utilities

```typescript
export function chunk<T>(array: T[], size: number): T[][] {
  return Array.from(
    { length: Math.ceil(array.length / size) },
    (_, i) => array.slice(i * size, i * size + size)
  )
}

export function groupBy<T, K extends keyof T>(
  array: T[],
  key: K
): Record<string, T[]> {
  return array.reduce((acc, item) => {
    const group = String(item[key])
    acc[group] = acc[group] ?? []
    acc[group].push(item)
    return acc
  }, {} as Record<string, T[]>)
}
```

---

## 📋 Type Reusability

### Shared Types

```typescript
// types/api.ts
export interface ApiResponse<T> {
  data: T
  error: string | null
}

export interface PaginatedResponse<T> {
  items: T[]
  total: number
  page: number
  pageSize: number
}
```

### Generic Components

```typescript
export function DataTable<T extends Entity>({
  data,
  columns,
  onRowClick
}: DataTableProps<T>) {
  // ... generic table implementation
}
```

---

## ✅ Reusability Checklist

- [ ] Researched existing implementation?
- [ ] Can extend existing component?
- [ ] Can use variant props?
- [ ] Can extract to utility?
- [ ] Is generic enough for reuse?
- [ ] Barrel export added?

